The protocol code confirms there’s no protocol-side minimum deposit beyond `underlyingAmount > 0`, and the buggy checkpoint path is exactly where expected. I’m tightening the verifier to a direct-execution-only version now, with profit measured from the actual claimed backlog token rather than any temporary funding path.
