I’m replacing `src/FlawVerifier.sol` with a direct-only verifier now. The edit keeps the exploit ordering unchanged: verify zero total stake, use verifier-held capital to become first new staker, force the first account checkpoint via `claimEarnings()`, then exit and report realized reward profit.
